\c 35
\s Ukulalela kwamaRekabi
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi elafika kuJeremiya livela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ensukwini zikaJehoyakhimi indodana kaJosiya, inkosi yakoJuda,\x + 25.1; 35.11.\x* lisithi:
\v 2 Yana endlini yamaRekabi,\x + 1 Lan. 2.55.\x* ukhulume lawo, uwalethe endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* kwelinye lamakamelo,\x + 35.4; 36.10. 1 Lan. 9.26,33; 23.28; 28.12. 2 Lan. 31.11. 1 Kho. 6.5.\x* uwanathise iwayini.
\v 3 Ngasengithatha uJahazaniya, indodana kaJeremiya, indodana kaHabaziniya, labafowabo, lawo wonke amadodana akhe, lendlu yonke yamaRekabi.
\v 4 Ngabaletha endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ekamelweni lamadodana kaHanani,\x + 35.4; 36.10. 1 Lan. 9.26,33; 23.28; 28.12. 2 Lan. 31.11. 1 Kho. 6.5.\x* indodana kaIgidaliya, umuntu kaNkulunkulu,\x + Dute. 33.1. Hlu. 13.6.\x* elaliseduze lekamelo leziphathamandla,\x + 35.4; 36.10. 1 Lan. 9.26,33; 23.28; 28.12. 2 Lan. 31.11. 1 Kho. 6.5.\x* elalingaphezu\x + 1 Kho. 6.6.\x* kwekamelo likaMahaseya,\x + 21.1; 29.25; 37.3.\x* indodana kaShaluma,\x + 32.7.\x* umlindimbundu.\x + 52.24. 2 Kho. 12.9; 25.18. 1 Lan. 9.19.\x*
\v 5 Ngasengibeka phambi kwamadodana endlu yamaRekabi izimbiza ezigcwele iwayini, lezinkezo, ngathi kibo: Nathani iwayini.
\v 6 Kodwa bathi: Kasilinathi iwayini, ngoba uJonadabi, indodana kaRekabi,\x + 2 Kho. 10.15,23.\x* ubaba, wasilaya esithi: Linganathi iwayini, lina labantwana benu, kuze kube nininini.
\v 7 Njalo lingakhi izindlu, lingahlanyeli inhlanyelo, lingahlanyeli izivini, lingabi lazo; kodwa lihlale emathenteni zonke insuku zenu, ukuze liphile insuku ezinengi ebusweni bomhlaba lapho elihlala khona njengabezizwe.\x + Eks. 20.12. Efe. 6.2,3.\x*
\v 8 Ngakho salilalela ilizwi likaJonadabi, indodana kaRekabi, ubaba, kukho konke asilaya ngakho, ukuthi singanathi iwayini zonke insuku zethu, thina, omkethu, amadodana ethu, lamadodakazi ethu;
\v 9 lokuthi singakhi izindlu zokuhlala kwethu; njalo singabi lesivini kumbe insimu kumbe inhlanyelo;
\v 10 kodwa sihlala emathenteni, silalele senze njengakho konke uJonadabi ubaba asilaya khona.
\v 11 Kodwa kwathi lapho uNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 46.2. 2 Kho. 24.1.\x* esenyukela elizweni, sathi: Wozani siye eJerusalema ngenxa yebutho lamaKhaladiya\x + 2 Kho. 24.2.\x* langenxa yebutho lamaSiriya.\x + 2 Kho. 24.2.\x* Sasesihlala eJerusalema.\x + 35 .7.\x*
\p
\v 12 Laselifika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuJeremiya lisithi:
\v 13 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Hamba uthi ebantwini bakoJuda lakwabahlali beJerusalema: Kaliyikwemukela yini ukulaywa ukuthi lilalele amazwi ami?\x + 5.3.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 14 Aqiniswa amazwi kaJonadabi, indodana kaRekabi, awalaya abantwana bakhe ukuthi banganathi iwayini; ngoba kaba\add li\add*nathanga kuze kube lamuhla, ngoba bawulalele umlayo kayise. Lami ngikhulumile kini ngivuke ngovivi ngikhuluma,\x + 2 Lan. 36.15.\x* kodwa kalingilalelanga.
\v 15 Futhi ngithume kini zonke inceku zami abaprofethi,\x + 2 Lan. 36.15.\x* ngivuka ngovivi ngi\add ba\add*thuma,\x + 2 Lan. 36.15.\x* ngisithi: Ake liphenduke, ngulowo lalowo endleleni yakhe embi,\x + 2 Kho. 17.13.\x* lenze izenzo zenu zibe zinhle,\x + 2 Kho. 17.13.\x* lingalandeli abanye onkulunkulu ukuthi libakhonze,\x + 25.6.\x* ukuze lihlale elizweni engalinika lina laboyihlo. Kodwa kalibekanga indlebe yenu,\x + 34.14.\x* kalilalelanga kimi.
\v 16 Ngoba amadodana kaJonadabi, indodana kaRekabi, awuqinisile umlayo kayise awalaya wona, kodwa lababantu kabangilaleli,
\v 17 ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Khangelani, ngizakwehlisela phezu kukaJuda laphezu kwabakhileyo bonke beJerusalema bonke ububi engibukhulume ngabo; ngoba ngikhulumile kibo, kodwa kabalalelanga, ngibabizile, kodwa kabaphendulanga.\x + Isai. 50.2.\x*
\p
\v 18 Lakuyo indlu yamaRekabi uJeremiya wathi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Ngenxa yokuthi lilalele umlayo kaJonadabi uyihlo, lagcina yonke imilayo yakhe, lenza njengakho konke alilaya khona,
\v 19 ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Kakuyikuqunywa muntu kuJonadabi indodana kaRekabi oma phambi kwami insuku zonke.\x + 15.1.\x*